msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "What were you like as a kid, Mama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Huh? That came out of nowhere."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "I used to dream of becoming a singer when I was a little girl."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Oh, niiice. A singer, huh? That's so you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Riiight? I'd always imagine standing under that spotlight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "I was sooo into stuff like that. I was meant for it, y'know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "If that's true, what are you doing at a place like this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Place like this...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "I mean, I wish I could've pursued it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "But I was too scared to audition... since I'm shy, y'know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "What'd you guys have a meeting about how to respond?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "That was a natural response, no meeting required."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "I've never thought of you as shy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Yeah, my first thought of you is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "That you're bold and full of energy, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "That's kinda why I come to this bar; you're fun to talk to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "You guys are gonna make me cry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Okay, let's move on..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "After all that praise...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Huh? What did you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I was thinking about something else..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Sheesh, I can't understand you sometimes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Whatever. So, why ask about my childhood?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "The thing is, I have a class reunion in a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "So I was curious about everyone else's childhoods."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Oh, that's what this was about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "I've never been to a class reunion. Have a good time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "You should head on over there. Stop wasting time here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "I still have some time so I'm good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Besides, I'm not sure if I wanna go..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "There's someone I really admired. I don't wanna see them look old."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Oh dear, but doesn't that kind of apply to you too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Truuue. How could you say that when you aged just as much?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "No one's gonna be shocked by my change."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Maybe you were strangely popular."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "That's a pretty nice thing to say...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Although \"strangely\" kinda bothers me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "So, you gonna go or what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Well, a part of me does want to go, I guess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "It's just a conflict between my memories and reality..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "What the hell are you talking about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Aren't you 30 this year? They should still be young, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "That's still really young."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Making yourself feel better, Mama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Eh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Y-You don't understand. They're not youthful anymore..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "How would you know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Because... the person I admired was my homeroom teacher!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Ohhh, that's who it is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Well, how do I put this...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "An adult with a lot of experience isn't so bad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "True."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Hm? What's going on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Oh sorry, I dozed off for a bit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "You should really lend him an ear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "You know, a baseball player married his friend's mom last year."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Oh, that should give you hope, Akiyoshi-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Eh? How so?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "What's important between a man and a woman is their feelings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Haven't I always told you not to be worried about age or looks?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "You haven't... How is any of this even relevant?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "He's saying age shouldn't matter!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "All right! A toast to Akiyoshi-kun's future prospects!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Oh, should we open a new sochu!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "You all just want a reason to drink."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Busted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Hahaha!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Anyway, you don't want to see your beloved teacher all aged up, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Well, to put it bluntly, yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Mmm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Go see them, Akiyoshi-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "All in all, you guys will reminisce and get along in no time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Is that how it usually goes? Was I getting worked up for nothing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Okay, I decided! I'll attend the class reunion!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Sounds like you made up your mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "So are you gonna keep your guard up from now on, Mama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Me? How come?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "If he gets closer to his teacher, he might stop coming here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "That makes no sense! What are you talking about!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Hmm, that would really hurt... my sales."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "What? Did you just say it'd hurt \"your sales?\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "You're imagining things. Here's to Akiyoshi-kun's lovely class reunion..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Cheeeeeers!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "I'm going to put a little more thought into this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "You're so indecisive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "I guess that just shows how much he treasures those memories."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Do what you gotta do, but make sure you don't regret it in the end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Y-You're so right. Haha..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "That was a rather dull ending..."
msgstr ""

